data.description: Recent updates on 12/23 include interior painting of walls, doors, and trim. New stove and new hot water tank. Other updates include new flooring upstairs (7/2023) and an updated septic system in 2021. Home on a large lot with mature landscaping, garage, and carport. Live close to town with the benefit of feeling like you are in the country. Open concept living. The main level boasts a primary suite with an en-suite bathroom, 2 additional bedrooms & 2nd bathroom. The lower level offers a large main room and a side area that could be a craft/office location. Close proximity to recreation, schools, and shopping.
